Hance, it should be proven that the damage we can output is enough to BALANCE the amount that we TAKE, giving us equal performance with other tanks.<br>
<br>
The argument against this is that RvR values offense over defense, so that if these two classes were so evenly matched, there would be no point in playing a polearmsman when you can kill casters much more effectively as a mercenary, and then still fight the Heroes nice and fairly, like.<br>
