<br>
A light tank should be able to be a primary tank in both a PvE and RvR group with equal ability of a heavy tank.  The difference comes in damage vs. defense.<br>
<br>
A light tank will do more damage allowing for a mob to die quicker at the cost of taking more damage during the fight vs. a heavy tank taking a bit longer to kill the mob but taking less damage during the fight.<br>
<br>
IF block and parry are working in RvR as they do in PvE now, you'll see a heavy tank able to fulfill his role against other tanks now.  None of the light tanks, unless you count savages, will be able to.  <br>
